Phu,

559
00:45:26,600 --> 00:45:27,930
Nava's at your house, right?

560
00:45:28,690 --> 00:45:29,470
Come out.

561
00:45:30,020 --> 00:45:31,370
Phraphai and I are at your door.

562
00:45:42,260 --> 00:45:42,790
What's going on?

563
00:45:43,820 --> 00:45:44,910
You've got some nerve asking that.

564
00:45:45,670 --> 00:45:46,200
Nava.

565
00:45:48,660 --> 00:45:50,250
You were the one who told him
to run away, weren't you?

566
00:45:52,840 --> 00:45:55,020
Phraphai, I...

567
00:45:56,470 --> 00:45:58,420
I came to see Phurich on my own.

568
00:46:00,970 --> 00:46:01,590
Nava,

569
00:46:02,440 --> 00:46:03,530
we already talked about this.

570
00:46:04,090 --> 00:46:05,060
I'm only doing this

571
00:46:05,500 --> 00:46:07,100
to keep you safe.

572
00:46:08,140 --> 00:46:11,060
You know how dangerous this is.

573
00:46:13,130 --> 00:46:13,900
That's right, Nava.

574
00:46:14,980 --> 00:46:16,140
We're only worried about you.

575
00:46:20,240 --> 00:46:21,220
But I feel trapped.

576
00:46:22,700 --> 00:46:24,160
I'm suffocating living like this.

577
00:46:25,020 --> 00:46:27,710
Nava,
I know you're feeling uncomfortable.

578
00:46:28,470 --> 00:46:29,450
But I have to do this.

579
00:46:30,210 --> 00:46:31,900
It's for your safety.

580
00:46:32,300 --> 00:46:33,830
This isn't a game, Nava.

581
00:46:34,690 --> 00:46:36,520
Otherwise, I wouldn't have let
Phraphai go this far.

582
00:46:40,640 --> 00:46:41,360
I'm sorry,

583
00:46:42,780 --> 00:46:44,360
but can someone tell me

584
00:46:45,100 --> 00:46:46,190
what's going on?

585
00:46:47,550 --> 00:46:50,250
You're all acting like
someone's trying to kidnap him.

586
00:46:51,510 --> 00:46:53,610
If there's something going on,
shouldn't you just tell me directly?

587
00:46:54,420 --> 00:46:56,020
Shut it.
This has nothing to do with you.

588
00:46:57,230 --> 00:47:00,240
Or maybe there's nothing going on.

589
00:47:01,400 --> 00:47:03,190
Maybe you're just trying to keep us apart.

590
00:47:04,190 --> 00:47:05,180
Is that all you can do?

591
00:47:06,290 --> 00:47:09,250
If that's all you've got,
then that's just pathetic.

592
00:47:09,770 --> 00:47:10,800
I'm about to lose my patience.

593
00:47:11,380 --> 00:47:13,150
You're an outsider, get out of here.

594
00:47:13,220 --> 00:47:14,040
Scram!

595
00:47:14,040 --> 00:47:15,150
- Phraphai!
- Hey!

596
00:47:15,830 --> 00:47:16,580
Phu, calm down.

597
00:47:20,490 --> 00:47:22,850
Phraphai, please stop.

598
00:47:28,720 --> 00:47:31,480
Nava, let's go home.

599
00:47:33,060 --> 00:47:34,920
I can't let you stay with someone like him.

600
00:47:41,300 --> 00:47:42,720
If you walk away with him right now,

601
00:47:44,470 --> 00:47:45,720
you'll never see me again.

602
00:47:47,800 --> 00:47:48,950
I've had enough of this!

603
00:47:57,760 --> 00:47:59,710
Can I talk to you Phraphai alone?

604
00:48:31,780 --> 00:48:34,220
I'm sorry, Phraphai,
for talking to you this way…

605
00:48:36,900 --> 00:48:38,530
But right now, I'm dating Mr. Phurich.

606
00:48:44,290 --> 00:48:45,710
I've fallen in love with him.

607
00:48:51,700 --> 00:48:52,720
I know

608
00:48:53,880 --> 00:48:56,440
everything you've done was for my sake,

609
00:48:59,760 --> 00:49:01,830
but if you really care about me…

610
00:49:04,120 --> 00:49:05,800
please let me follow my heart.

611
00:49:09,790 --> 00:49:10,340
Mm.

612
00:49:12,670 --> 00:49:13,280
Nava.

613
00:49:17,060 --> 00:49:20,650
After hearing that, what else can I say?

614
00:49:26,990 --> 00:49:29,310
What I said might sound selfish,

615
00:49:31,760 --> 00:49:33,620
but it's how I truly feel.

616
00:49:38,440 --> 00:49:42,100
So you've chosen to be with Mr. Phurich?

617
00:49:49,460 --> 00:49:49,980
Yes.

618
00:49:56,910 --> 00:49:58,730
What about tonight, then?

619
00:49:59,640 --> 00:50:01,140
We still have to cleanse the poison together.

620
00:50:06,690 --> 00:50:08,490
I'll do it myself tonight.

621
00:50:10,520 --> 00:50:11,790
You don't have to worry.

622
00:50:47,370 --> 00:50:48,960
Thank you for understanding me.

623
00:50:50,670 --> 00:50:52,600
Alright we'll talk later.

624
00:50:54,090 --> 00:50:55,160
I just need to take this call.

625
00:50:57,960 --> 00:50:58,410
Sure.

626
00:51:42,860 --> 00:51:43,480
Yes.

627
00:52:03,740 --> 00:52:04,890
Met, get in the car.

628
00:52:06,090 --> 00:52:08,260
Hey! Phraphai! What's going on? Wait!

629
00:52:08,980 --> 00:52:09,680
Phraphai!

630
00:52:21,990 --> 00:52:22,770
What did you just say, Lek?

631
00:52:24,880 --> 00:52:25,340
Huh?

632
00:52:27,120 --> 00:52:28,250
Who came looking for me?

633
00:52:42,190 --> 00:52:42,720
Dad!

634
00:52:46,290 --> 00:52:46,840
Dad!

635
00:52:48,260 --> 00:52:48,860
Dad!

636
00:52:50,340 --> 00:52:50,910
Dad!

637
00:53:06,700 --> 00:53:09,990
Who did this to you? Who?

638
00:53:26,920 --> 00:53:28,220
Was it the humans?

639
00:53:30,540 --> 00:53:31,630
I'll handle this myself.

640
00:53:47,290 --> 00:53:49,130
(Love each other.)

641
00:53:50,980 --> 00:53:52,800
(Complicated.)

642
00:53:54,950 --> 00:53:56,280
(My world.)

643
00:53:57,280 --> 00:53:59,920
(A new world together.)

644
00:54:02,230 --> 00:54:04,140
(Couple.)

645
00:54:05,920 --> 00:54:08,780
(What is important?)

646
00:54:09,600 --> 00:54:10,160
Mom.

647
00:54:10,160 --> 00:54:11,760
(Next Episode)

648
00:54:11,870 --> 00:54:13,660
There's something I need to tell you, ma'am.

649
00:54:16,200 --> 00:54:17,300
I'm in love with your son.

650
00:54:19,630 --> 00:54:20,910
There's something important I have to say.

651
00:54:21,680 --> 00:54:22,440
From now on,

652
00:54:22,660 --> 00:54:24,000
Nava won't be working here anymore.

653
00:54:24,650 --> 00:54:27,100
And as for you, stay away from him,

654
00:54:27,950 --> 00:54:29,360
or I'll make sure you regret it.

655
00:54:31,030 --> 00:54:32,660
I can't lose someone I love again

656
00:54:34,580 --> 00:54:35,570
especially you, Nava.

657
00:54:36,660 --> 00:54:40,160
I promise I'll protect you
with everything I have.

658
00:54:41,440 --> 00:54:43,370
From now on, I'll go with you.

659
00:54:44,690 --> 00:54:46,980
Phurich, I get how you feel.

660
00:54:47,660 --> 00:54:48,940
But you need to calm down first, man.

661
00:54:51,080 --> 00:54:51,870
Get back!

662
00:54:52,160 --> 00:54:52,950
Phraphai.

663
00:54:53,950 --> 00:54:55,320
They're going to kill Nava.

664
00:55:00,510 --> 00:55:01,500
Hey! What the hell are you doing?

665
00:55:14,490 --> 00:55:19,400
♪ The sky... that looks so vast, ♪

666
00:55:19,950 --> 00:55:23,800
♪ with the sea that I see as vast. ♪

667
00:55:25,570 --> 00:55:29,320
♪ Just looking at the waves every day.
There's no way we'll meet. ♪

668
00:55:29,320 --> 00:55:34,430
♪ Our hearts... that beat together. ♪

669
00:55:35,220 --> 00:55:38,680
♪ But the world never listens. ♪

670
00:55:40,360 --> 00:55:44,210
♪ It's just a parallel line waiting for a miracle. ♪

671
00:55:44,210 --> 00:55:51,160
♪ Even though in reality... there are many rules.
